<h1>About Us:</h1>
Welcome to the world of JavaJam. This up in coming coffee shop is the place to be if you enjoy a great cup of joe, music, or poetry. Here at JavaJam, we work to make this place a second home. Juilo Perez, the owner here at the JavaJam Coffee House, has put his heart and soul into this place.
<br>
